
<!DOCTYPE html>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Text [utility] - SUIT CSS</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1, width=device-width">

<style>
  html {
    color: black;
  }

  .dev-Box {
    background: #ddd;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    max-width: 400px;
  }
</style>

<div class="Test">
  <h1 class="Test-title">SUIT CSS: <a href="https://github.com/suitcss/utils-text">text utilities</a> tests</h1>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textBreak</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">breaks stings across multiple lines, when they are wider than the container</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box u-textBreak">
        http://subdomain.exampledomain.com/averylongurlthatneedstobebrokenotherwiseitisgoingtokeepgoingforever
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3 class="Test-it">does not break strings that are not wider than the container</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box u-textBreak">
        wraplongwords dontbreaklongwords
        wraplongwords dontbreaklongwords
        wraplongwords dontbreaklongwords
        wraplongwords dontbreaklongwords
        wraplongwords dontbreaklongwords
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textCenter</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">center-aligns text</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box u-textCenter">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textLeft</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">left-aligns text</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box u-textLeft">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textRight</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">right-aligns text</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box u-textRight">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textInheritColor</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">should inherit the ancestral text color</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box">
      <a class="u-textInheritColor" href="#non">Should always be black</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textKern</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">should enable kerning in supported browsers</h3>
  <div class="Test-run" style="font-family:arial;font-size:20px">
    <div>The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog (default)</div>
    <div class="u-textKern">The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog (kerning enabled)</div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textNoWrap</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">should not wrap text</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box u-textNoWrap">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla hendrerit blandit dolor, at euismod ante eleifend in. Duis imperdiet cursus nibh, quis tincidunt nibh rhoncus at.
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="Test-describe">.u-textTruncate</h2>
  <h3 class="Test-it">clips and truncates a single line of text, using an ellipsis</h3>
  <div class="Test-run">
    <div class="dev-Box u-textTruncate">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla hendrerit blandit dolor, at euismod ante eleifend in. Duis imperdiet cursus nibh, quis tincidunt nibh rhoncus at.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
